# Pre-commit hook — intentionally minimal.
#
# We run lint + typecheck in CI against the PR diff rather than every local
# commit. Blocking the commit loop on a 20-30s typecheck slows iteration to
# a crawl, and developers end up reflexively --no-verify'ing, which defeats
# the point. Keep this hook cheap.
#
# If we later want pre-commit lint against STAGED files only (not the whole
# repo), wire in lint-staged here. Until then this is a no-op.

exit 0
